{
  "stem": "17337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A stone fell through-- through the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and it fell not far from-- from-- from the bed where my mother was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, in the beginning, you are afraid to walk to the window because you don't know what's happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But finally, the following day, we found out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, Bochnia was a town-- salt-- salt mines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the workers what were going home in the middle of the night from the-- from the night shift or whatever, they got drunk.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they just throw rocks, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It must be for fun or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember, the police came the following day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they tried to smooth it that we shouldn't make no complaints, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't wanna do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They did it just because they were drunk, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and I don't think so they-- they did anything against them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I imagine there must be other-- other times when there must have have some problems.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I wouldn't remember, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was too young for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Well, I imagine my worst thing was when my grandparents passed away, because they were like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the closest family, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- my grandfather was like my father, you know, because I was brought up by them, you know, in one house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- and I miss them very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How about a happier time?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we used to-- I used to have six uncles and three aunts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] And I remember, during the summer, I used to go for vacation spent by them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to send their children, the cousins, what used to come to spend the summer by us.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
